headline: What to Expect From Viatris' Next Quarterly Earnings Report
summary: Viatris is all set to release its fiscal second-quarter earnings next month, and analysts project a double-digit earnings drop.

headline: Covering The Flaws In The Viatris Undervaluation Argument
summary: Viatris remains a value play with low valuation and high free cash flow, but growth is hampered by legacy drug price erosion and lack of innovation.
